A phenomenon that occurs in the heavenly bodies just before the coming of Yeshua, the sun darkens and the moon changes like blood.

- Yeshua Coming -

Joel 2:31 KJV......

31 The sun shall be turned into darkness, and the moon into blood, before the great and terrible day of the Lord come.

Matthew 24:28~31 KJV......

28 For wheresoever the carcase is, there will the eagles be gathered together.
29 Immediately after the tribulation of those days shall the sun be darkened, and the moon shall not give her light, and the stars shall fall from heaven, and the powers of the heavens shall be shaken:
30 And then shall appear the sign of the Son of man in heaven: and then shall all the tribes of the earth mourn, and they shall see the Son of man coming in the clouds of heaven with power and great glory.
31 And he shall send his angels with a great sound of a trumpet, and they shall gather together his elect from the four winds, from one end of heaven to the other.

Mark 13:24~27 KJV......

24 But in those days, after that tribulation, the sun shall be darkened, and the moon shall not give her light,
25 And the stars of heaven shall fall, and the powers that are in heaven shall be shaken.
26 And then shall they see the Son of man coming in the clouds with great power and glory.
27 And then shall he send his angels, and shall gather together his elect from the four winds, from the uttermost part of the earth to the uttermost part of heaven.

Revelation 6:12~17 KJV......

12 And I beheld when he had opened the sixth seal, and, lo, there was a great earthquake; and the sun became black as sackcloth of hair, and the moon became as blood;
13 And the stars of heaven fell unto the earth, even as a fig tree casteth her untimely figs, when she is shaken of a mighty wind.
14 And the heaven departed as a scroll when it is rolled together; and every mountain and island were moved out of their places.
15 And the kings of the earth, and the great men, and the rich men, and the chief captains, and the mighty men, and every bondman, and every free man, hid themselves in the dens and in the rocks of the mountains;
16 And said to the mountains and rocks, Fall on us, and hide us from the face of him that sitteth on the throne, and from the wrath of the Lamb:
17 For the great day of his wrath is come; and who shall be able to stand?

One day before the coming of Yeshua, the sun gets dark and the moon changes like a blood.

In the era of more than 2000 years, there were no astronomical telescopes, and they would have simply conveyed what they had heard and seen through visions and words.

God continued to show me the vision that Nibiru System is coming in 2017, 2018, 2019, 2020, 2021, 2022.

Nibiru is a system like a solar system, with a red planet and a white planet in it.

The white planet is an incredibly large planet. The color appeared to be sparkling white. And the red planet is red in color. That's why I call it the Red Planet.

Because of this Nibiru system, there are changes in the Sun, Moon, and just before the coming of Yeshua, the sun turns black and the moon turns like blood.

And now, the whole world sees a partially pink sky, when the time comes, the sky all over the world will be completely covered in deep pink, and when that time comes, even the air will appear purple, then the axis of the North and South Poles will change. God continued to give me a vision. These phenomena are to occur just before the coming of Yeshua.

Nibiru is coming.

There are LOTS OF Uyghur restaurants all over China. I am not making it up. The whole story of China prosecuting Uyghur is total fabrication, just like what they did with the White Helmet story in Syria. You must understand, the Western Media is a fully controlled propaganda machine. When they get the directive to run the Uyghur agenda, pitting Chinese against Muslims, they are in full force operations from every single Western Media institution with a collective voice.

The real story behind Uyghur is that in around 1990s, there were massive fundamentalist movements in the Xinjiang region for independence to create a Pan Turkistan empire from Turkey to Xinjiang. I don't know who were behind those movements, but it caused quite some bloodshed. As a result, there was iron hand oppression in the region, arresting lots of fundamentalists or separatists. At that time, the West was waging war in Middle East and the arrests were ignores. Eventually the separatist movements died out. And around 2010, the Chinese government started a campaign to educate the local people, including the Uyghur (there are many ethnic groups in the region) for vocational skills. The rational is that if the people in the region have a skill set and make a better life, it will be less likely that they will be drawn to fundamentalist teaching. Now China being China, they set up massive education schools to house the students, providing anything they need for the education. At the beginning, it was not picked up by the Western Media propaganda machine. But around 2015, even before Trump era, the story has been picked up and changed to be "forced labor". And during the Trump era, the narrative is further changed to "Gen o c ide."

It is interesting to observe that most Muslim countries side with China, knowing full well that the Western Media is trying to drive a wedge between Chinese and Muslim.
